<p><strike>2/12/17</strike><br/>report them<br/>2/12/17<br/>Bitterly cold this morning had to stand out &amp; listen to the display by the Prince at the chaps caught smoking in Barracks  beautiful 48 hours light punishment.  snow fell about dinner time [indecipherable] in as many minutes then rain soon afterwards snow again</p>
<p>3/12/17<br/>Late last night snow fell heavily with a driving wind with it.  Bitterly cold when snow stopped but not for long snow was driven just like dust in fact it came in bursts.  the snow is about 5 inches thick but in place when wind swept same round about two feet.</p>
<p>4/12/17<br/>German report to hand taken 4000 pris 60 guns 100 machine gun from British near Cambria a day or so ago.</p>
